PrecisAuthority to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT to amend the CANADA-NOVA SCOTIA COOPERATION AGREEMENT ON ECONOMIC DIVERSIFICATION for the purpose of increasing the funding allocated to projects in the fields of telecommunications, transportation, infrastructure, information technologies, tourism and waterfront development, and to increase the size of the Management Committee from two to four voting members.
Attachments
precis:
Authority to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT to amend the
CANADA-NOVA SCOTIA COOPERATION AGREEMENT ON ECONOMIC DIVERSIFICATION for
the purpose of increasing the funding allocated to projects in the fields
of telecommunications, transportation, infrastructure, information
technologies, tourism and waterfront development, and to increase the size
of the Management Committee from two to four voting members.
